title: Parrotheads party it up in Irvine
text: Parrotheads party it up in Irvine Oct. 25, 2015 Updated 11:58 a.m. 1 of 44 Jimmy Buffett fans clad in island-theme attire belt karaoke songs in the parking lot of Irvine Meadows Amphitheater on Saturday before Jimmy Buffett's concert. , NICK AGRO, STAFF PHOTOGRAPHER 1 of 44 Jimmy Buffett performs at Irvine Meadows Amphitheater on Saturday. , KELLY A. SWIFT, CONTRIBUTING PHOTOGRAPHER 1 of 44 An RV parked outside Saturday's Jimmy Buffett concert at Irvine Meadows Amphitheater.
